quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  54,41,Netoto Abekanyilisi betsela Abandu ba Firaun
  54,42,"Bakhaya ebimanyisio biefu biosi pe, mana nikhubatila omutilo kwa amaani kwobunyali"
  54,43,Ne Abakhayi benyu bali nende amani okhushila abo baranjilila nohomba kahandikwa mubitabu mbu enywe mubule okhufunaanibwa
  54,44,"Nohomba baboolanga mbu: ‘‘efwe khuli abaanji khulishila butswa.’’"
  54,45,Abanji abo balashilwa ne balakalukha inyuma tsimbilo
  54,46,"Halali inyanga yeyindukho niyabalakwa, Ne indukho ni isiro muno mana khandi indulu pa"
  54,47,Toto Abetsimbi balimubukori nende mubulalu
  54,48,"Inyanga yabaliswerululwa mafumama nibasukunwa mumulilo, baliboolelwa mbu : ‘‘pile omulilo kwa Jahanam.’’"
  54,49,Ne toto buli eshindu khwaloonga khushichelo
  54,50,"Ne likhuwa liefu nililala butwa, shinga okhulimba no khulimbula tsimoni"
  54,51,Ne toto khwasishia abashienywe alikho mwinywe uparanga
  54,52,Ne koosi kabakhola kali mubitabu
  54,53,Liosi liosi lititi nende likhonga liahandikwa
  54,54,Toto balia baria Nyasaye baliba mwikulu mumikunda chilimwo emialo
  54,55,"Mushikhalo shiatoto, ewo Omwami Omunyali"